International Healthcare Solutions revenue growth to be in the range of 1 to 4 percent, up from the previous range of a
3 percent decline to flat;
Adjusted Diluted Earnings P er Share to be in the range of $11.85 to $11.95, representing growth of 7 to 8 percent, raised from
